# PCA C
Principle Component Analysis using C from scratch

This program used GNU Scientific Library gsl 2.3.0.2779

## Usage
`k` is the desired dimension of reduced dataset.

```
Usage: pca-compute filename k
```

## Sample
Command:
```
pca-compute test 2
```
